      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is a solid and reliable performer that has been well-cared for, making it a great choice for your next daily driver. It runs beautifully and offers a comfortable ride with plenty of great miles ahead. It\u2019s in good shape overall and ready for its next adventure\u2014come take a look!",
