    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational. While there are some minor exterior scuffs and light wear on the driver's seat consistent with its age, the car remains mechanically sound and ready for its next owner.",
