    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a donor for parts. It currently has major mechanical failures, including a transmission that slips significantly and an engine that requires an immediate overhaul to be reliable. Cosmetically, the body shows signs of heavy oxidation and several deep dents, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. Please note that the vehicle is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 3800.0,
